sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant DetailPage as Lab Detail Route /lab/[slug]
    participant ContentAPI as GET /api/blogs/:slug or /api/projects/:slug
    participant MetricsAPI as POST /api/overview/views
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Visitor->>DetailPage: Open /lab/{slug}
    DetailPage->>ContentAPI: Request content by slug
    ContentAPI->>DB: Find article or project by slug
    DB-->>ContentAPI: Content record
    ContentAPI-->>DetailPage: Renderable payload
    DetailPage-->>Visitor: Display full article/project

    par Track engagement
        DetailPage->>MetricsAPI: Send view event with slug and kind
        MetricsAPI->>DB: Increment views counter
        DB-->>MetricsAPI: Updated metric
        MetricsAPI-->>DetailPage: Ack
    and Keep page interactive
        Visitor->>DetailPage: Scroll and interact with links
    end
